# Lead Generation Plan

## Objective
You said there are no leads yet, so build a lead engine alongside the inbox agent.

## Safe first lead channels
1. Founder-led outbound email to warmish operators/business owners you can identify manually
2. LinkedIn prospecting list builder (manual first, then semi-automated enrichment)
3. Founder content funnel from LinkedIn/X/Substack/Medium/Facebook
4. Simple landing form that routes inbound interest to Gmail + Supabase
5. Referral asks from existing personal/business contacts

## First lead gen agent to build
### Prospect Research Agent
Purpose:
- take a company/person URL or name
- research source/company/context
- create a lead record
- generate a one-paragraph personalization brief
- suggest outreach angle
- never auto-send at first

Inputs:
- name
- title
- company
- website/linkedin
- location

Outputs:
- ICP fit score
- personalization notes
- outreach angle
- draft email opening line
- next step

## ICP starting point
Priority:
- business owners with liquid capital
- operators/founders already interested in systematic trading
- higher-income professionals with account sizes >= target band
- referrals and 2nd-degree connections

## Lead sources to stand up today
- one Supabase landing page form: name, email, account size band, goals, risk tolerance, source
- one Google Calendar booking CTA in all posts
- one founder bio link that points to waitlist + booking link
- manual list of 25 prospects from personal network + local contacts + social interactions

## Daily target
- 10 researched prospects added
- 5 custom outreach drafts
- 1 founder post on LinkedIn
- 2 X posts
- 1 Substack or Medium article every 3-4 days
